company_name: PLEXCOM GESMBH - GREENTENDER GMBH PLEXIGLASVERARBEITUNG UND DISPLAYBAU
information: The company PLEXCOM GESMBH - GREENTENDER GMBH PLEXIGLASVERARBEITUNG UND DISPLAYBAU, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, which operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry industry. It is based in Leonding, Austria.
